---
title: BBQ Black Bean & Chicken Lettuce Wraps with Pineapple Salsa & Crispy Onions
description: Sweet and savory is a combination we can always get behind! The sweet and savory lettuce wraps in this 15-minute meal are fully loaded in the best possible way: BBQ black beans tossed with caramelized onion and green pepper, topped with melty mozzarella, finished with juicy pineapple salsa, and showered with crispy fried onions for crunchy contrast. Have you ever heard of luckier lettuce leaves? (We’ll wait…)
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/657986a1bb715086aa4d04fb-9d9adc5c.jpeg
